According to one of the [Atlassian's Developers documentation|https://docs.atlassian.com/confluence/4.1.5/com/atlassian/confluence/pages/persistence/dao/WebDavAttachmentDao.html], WebDAV attachment storage is deprecated since 2.7. 

However in the [WebDAV configuration doc|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Configuring+a+WebDAV+client+for+Confluence] it does not clarify that this is actually deprecated, which could make some users confused when trying to use it. 

This is a suggestion to insert the message about it being deprecated in the documentation.
